'''Autopunch''' is an automatic record punch in feature for Logic.

To use Autopunch in Logic do the following.

[[Logic: Record to an audio track|Record enable]] a track in Logic.

Select the '''Autopunch''' button from the transport so that it is red [[File:Logic autopunch icon.png]]

Create a cycle using the ''bottom half'' (autopunch markers) of the time display bar.



[[File:Logic autopunch markers.png]]



When you [[Logic: Record to an audio track|begin recording]] Logic will only record within the time span of the autopunch markers.


